question: Taun pira 'net interest income excluding cib markets' paling dhuwur?
Pinten jumlah CIB Markets Net Interest Income, ing yuta, saking 2014 dumugi 2016?
Kanggo taun 2015, pinten pikolih bunga resi saking segmen ingkang gadhah aset bunga rata-rata paling andhap?
Mangga dipunandharaken tren saking 'net interest yield on average interest-earning assets excluding cib markets' wiwit taun 2014 dumugi 2016.
answer: The net interest yield on average interest-earning assets excluding CIB markets first decreased from 2.53% in 2014 to 2.49% in 2015, and then saw a significant increase to 2.59% in 2016, finishing the period at its highest point.

question: Sebutaken taun-taun pundi ingkang 'net interest income 2013 managed basis'ipun langkung kathah tinimbang $45.000 yuta.
Kanggo taun 2016, pinten persen saka 'aset bunga sing rata-rata' sing dumadi saka 'aset bunga pasar cib rata-rata'?

Menawi Pendhetan Bunga Resik menika asil saking Sembah Bewara Bunga Resik saha Aset Kaanggo Bunga Rata-rata, pinten 'pendhetan bunga resik cib markets' ing taun 2014 menawi sembah bewara nipun 1,25 tinimbang 1,15? (Sadayane wilangan ing yuta)

Padosi gayutan antawisipun pertumbuhan 'total rata-rata aset ingkang ngasilaken bunga' lan owah-owahan 'net interest yield ingkang dipunpendhet saking rata-rata aset ingkang ngasilaken bunga ing basis ingkang dipunkelola' salebeting wekdal tigang taun.
answer: Boten wonten gayutan langsung ingkang ajeg. Saking taun 2014 ngantos 2015, total rata-rata aset ingkang ngasilaken bunga tuwuh nalika net interest yield mandhap. Nanging, saking taun 2015 ngantos 2016, aset saha yield sami minggah. Gayutan ingkang owah-ganti punika nedahaken bilih faktor sanesipun saking kathahipun aset total mangaribawani net interest yield.

question: Sanes pundi kalih item baris wonten ing tabel ingkang dipunandharaken kanthi cetha minangka panggurangi saking total sakderengipun, dhedhasar andharaning deskripsi?
answer: less : cib markets net interest income ( c )
less : average cib markets interest-earning assets ( c )
